The good news: I have completed another scenario and added it to my 
set, #138.

More good news: I am going to start working on #139-149.  These won't 
be as complicated as some previous ones were.

Bad news: #150 is probably going to be renumbered 151.  For those of 
you have been through that scenario number, oh well.

More bad news: I won't be releasing any scenarios until I get quite a 
few more completed just to make sure I have ideas for every scenario # 
I have completed.

Mixed news: If I keep the numbers up, I will end up with over 50 
scenarios in this set.
